{"tid":2030289,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"我係美國魔法學生, 即將去霍格華茲Exchange ,呢度生活如何 ?","createTime":"2020-05-22T16:02:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-29T01:29:23.000Z","uid":353419,"like":1,"dislike":23,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"485bad3f20c5eb812b1da5e9a3a81b96e00dc45c","tid":2030289,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T16:02:57.000Z","msg":"我係伊爾弗莫尼魔法學校的二年班生，<br />\n當年係美國追捕葛林戴華德果班正氣師 ，大部份係我學校畢業。<br />\n<br />\n暑假後即將去霍格華茲留學一年，好擔心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。聽講你地學校有條蛇襲擊學生, 又有地獄三頭犬， 山怪同埋巨型蜘蛛。我好不安<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/dust.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。仲有你地曾經請左個神棍作家教黑魔法防御術，究竟呢間學校學唔學到野?<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n你地當年有個學生係美國放哂啲怪獸搗亂，都係靠我地美國巫師收恰 ！其實霍格華茲係咪吹大左?<br />\n<br />\n請各位霍格華茲同學分享下你地既校園生活<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a80b698a8a31f0de0c76861f5f9cc1cd09ae602e","tid":2030289,"uid":249885,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T19:23:28.000Z","msg":"fuckerwalktz 都ok 嘅 叫差過我地恒大少少 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n今年比較多nds 啲course 轉左用普通話教<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n同埋要留意翻捲舌發音<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 如果唔係有機會出唔到法術<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0971e74b991398ac37b41f4ca29d5b06b8e8aeb","tid":2030289,"uid":258578,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T19:34:48.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6def08b520da2f9196d74031923ed2fb3e2786b4","tid":2030289,"uid":87257,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-22T19:54:52.000Z","msg":"update吓好喎, mate。我地師兄Potter未grad就同其他師兄師姐，搞掂咗佛地魔，依家做埋神科---黑魔法lecturer添啦。不知幾多exchange嘅過黎就係為咗想上佢嘅堂。我驚你到時sit堂都冇位